OL,9,Fskull fractures with a hammer in July
OL,10,Flast year in .
OL,12,FDoorbell footage shows Norgrove
OL,13,Fentering the property and leaving
OL,14,Fagain, packing his car up moments
OL,15,Fafter killing Ms Gordon.
