OL,3,CDaughter of woman beaten to death by
OL,4,Cher builder deplores his sentence
OL,6,FThe recently qualified bricklayer, who
OL,7,Fmet Ms Gordon through a mutual friend
OL,8,Fat the Jehovah's Witnesses Kingdom
OL,9,FHall they attended, was paid #29,000
OL,10,Fand agreed to build the extension
OL,11,Fwithin two months.
OL,13,FRhian Brown, Ms Gordon's daughter, has
OL,14,Fsaid the manner of her death and the
OL,15,Fsentence handed to her killer has made
OL,16,Fit impossible to remember the better
OL,17,Ftimes with her mother.
