OL,3,CDaughter of woman beaten to death by
OL,4,Cher builder deplores his sentence
OL,6,F"The way that she died and her last
OL,7,Fmoments it's so hard, it's hard to
OL,8,Fthink of, it's hard to imagine. He
OL,9,Fknew what he was going to do when he
OL,10,Fwent into that house," she said.
OL,12,F"And he knew, my mom didn't know but
OL,13,Fhe knew that she didn't have a chance."
OL,15,FRhian added that "it doesn't make
OL,16,Fsense" that Norgrove was given a
OL,17,Fminimum term of 15 years.
OL,19,F"I don't know what this man thinks or
OL,20,Fbelieves but it's not the same thing
OL,21,Fas my mother.
