OL,10,F"How is that justice?
OL,12,F'I just know I walked out of there on
OL,13,Fthat day feeling like justice hadn't
OL,14,Fbeen served'
OL,16,F"It doesn't make sense to me. I mean
OL,17,Fit just doesn't give you any sort of
OL,18,Fconfidence or make you feel that the
