OL,6,FPassing sentence on Wednesday, January
OL,7,F31, Judge Chambers said the "brutal
OL,8,Fand savage" offence, involving eight
OL,9,Fblows to the head, was aggravated by a
OL,10,Ffalse statement Norgrove gave police
OL,11,Fsaying his victim was alive and well
OL,12,Fwhen he left the property.
OL,14,FThe judge told Norgrove, a former
OL,15,Fpublic sector worker: "You used a
OL,16,Fhammer to repeatedly strike her to the
OL,17,Fhead.
OL,19,F"You were angry because she had
OL,20,Fcontinued to criticise you for your
OL,21,Fchronic delays and workmanship."
